### Weighted Sum of Three Poses

Blend across three targets: `idle`, `crouch`, `jump`. Weights sum to `1.0`.

```scheme
(define (blend-3 ax bx cx wa wb wc)
  (+ (* ax wa)
     (* bx wb)
     (* cx wc)))

(motion
 (pose
  (entity 'figure
          (transform
           100.0
           (blend-3 150.0 100.0 200.0 0.5 0.3 0.2)
           0.0))))
```

At `wa=0.5`, `wb=0.3`, `wc=0.2`: mostly idle height, some crouch, a touch of jump.

[VISUAL: Figure at y ≈ 145, blending the three vertical offsets.]

