### Crossfade Window

Transition over a fixed time window while both animations continue to play.

```scheme
(define (idle-angle t)
  (* 5.0 (sin (* 4.0 t))))

(define (reach-angle t)
  (+ 60.0 (* 10.0 (sin (* 2.0 t)))))

(define (ease-in-out x)
  (- (* 3.0 x x)
     (* 2.0 x x x)))

(define (blend-x ax bx w)
  (+ (* ax (- 1.0 w))
     (* bx w)))

(motion
 (at 0.0
     (pose
      (entity 'arm
              (joint 'shoulder
                     (blend-x (idle-angle 0.0)
                              (reach-angle 0.0)
                              (ease-in-out 0.0))
                     0.0))))
 (at 0.25
     (pose
      (entity 'arm
              (joint 'shoulder
                     (blend-x (idle-angle 0.25)
                              (reach-angle 0.25)
                              (ease-in-out 0.5))
                     0.0))))
 (at 0.5
     (pose
      (entity 'arm
              (joint 'shoulder
                     (blend-x (idle-angle 0.5)
                              (reach-angle 0.5)
                              (ease-in-out 1.0))
                     0.0)))))
```

[VISUAL: Arm oscillates gently (idle), then over 0.5 seconds the oscillation shifts to the larger reach amplitude and slower frequency.]

