### Layered Blend: Additive Offset

Instead of replacing, add a second animation on top of the base (common for gestures).

```scheme
(define (base-y t)
  (* 10.0 (sin (* 4.0 t))))

(define (gesture-y t)
  (* 20.0 (sin (* 12.0 t))))

(define (additive-blend base gesture w)
  (+ base (* gesture w)))

(motion
 (at 0.0
     (pose
      (entity 'hand
              (transform
               100.0
               (additive-blend (base-y 0.0) (gesture-y 0.0) 0.0)
               0.0))))
 (at 1.0
     (pose
      (entity 'hand
              (transform
               100.0
               (additive-blend (base-y 1.0) (gesture-y 1.0) 0.5)
               0.0))))
 (at 2.0
     (pose
      (entity 'hand
              (transform
               100.0
               (additive-blend (base-y 2.0) (gesture-y 2.0) 1.0)
               0.0)))))
```

[VISUAL: Gentle bob grows a high-frequency shake layered on top.]

