### Blend with Root-Motion Extraction

When blending two locomotion clips, extract the root displacement from each and blend it separately to avoid foot-slide.

```scheme
(define (walk-a-root t)
  (* 80.0 t))

(define (walk-b-root t)
  (* 120.0 t))

(define (blend-x ax bx w)
  (+ (* ax (- 1.0 w))
     (* bx w)))

(motion
 (at 0.0
     (pose
      (entity 'figure
              (transform
               (blend-x (walk-a-root 0.0) (walk-b-root 0.0) 0.0)
               100.0
               0.0))))
 (at 1.0
     (pose
      (entity 'figure
              (transform
               (blend-x (walk-a-root 1.0) (walk-b-root 1.0) 0.5)
               100.0
               0.0))))
 (at 2.0
     (pose
      (entity 'figure
              (transform
               (blend-x (walk-a-root 2.0) (walk-b-root 2.0) 1.0)
               100.0
               0.0)))))
```

