### Blend Two Forces

Gravity pulls down; magnetic pull attracts sideways. Blend the acceleration vectors.

```scheme
(define (gravity-ay) -100.0)
(define (magnet-ay) 0.0)
(define (magnet-ax) 80.0)

(define (blend-x ax bx w)
