### Blend Two Secondary-Motion Delays

Hair A lags by 0.1 seconds. Hair B lags by 0.3 seconds. Blend the lag magnitude.

```scheme
(define (head-x t)
  (+ 150.0 (* 50.0 (sin (* 3.0 t)))))

(define (hair-x head-t lag)
  (head-x (- head-t lag)))

(define (blend-x ax bx w)
  (+ (* ax (- 1.0 w))
     (* bx w)))

(motion
 (at 0.5
     (pose
      (entity 'head (transform (head-x 0.5) 100.0 0.0))
      (entity 'hair
