### Blend Two Footstep-Impact Magnitudes

Step A has 40-pixel impact. Step B has 10-pixel impact (tiptoe). Blend the bounce height.

```scheme
(define (impact-y t mag)
  (let ((phase (- t (floor t))))
    (if (< phase 0.1)
        (* mag (- 1.0 (/ phase 0.1)))
        0.0)))

(define (blend-x ax bx w)
  (+ (* ax (- 1.0 w))
     (* bx w)))

(motion
 (at 0.0
     (pose
      (entity 'foot
              (transform
               100.0
               (+ 50.0 (blend-x (impact-y 0.0 40.0) (impact-y 0.0 10.0) 0.5))
               0.0))))
 (at 0.5
     (pose
      (entity 'foot
              (transform
               100.0
               (+ 50.0 (blend-x (impact-y 0.5 40.0) (impact-y 0.5 10.0) 0.5))
               0.0))))
 (at 1.0
     (pose
      (entity 'foot
              (transform
               100.0
               (+ 50.0 (blend-x (impact-y 1.0 40.0) (impact-y 1.0 10.0) 0.5))
               0.0)))))
```

[VISUAL: Foot bounces 25 pixels on impact, halfway between heavy and light steps.]

